# diagnosing-bugs

Full workflow: `.claude/skills/diagnosing-bugs/SKILL.md`.

Loop: reproduce (minimal, deterministic) → minimize → hypothesize (specific, falsifiable) → instrument (smallest logging needed) → fix (smallest change for the confirmed cause) → test (any Critical-tier reward-math bug needs a regression test pinning the old-wrong-value to correct).

Triage first: wrong output from the Reward Knowledge/Valuation/Optimization/Simulation Engines is Critical — stop and fix before anything else. Never patch a calculation bug by adjusting the AI narration layer instead of the underlying deterministic logic.
